        <abstract>
            <p>Movement of cotton plant cotyledons.</p> 
<p>Thanks JDH for his praise of <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Delighted that JDH is thinking about geographical distribution, wishes he would go over the New Zealand flora again.</p>
